    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Long tap on the home screen of the device.\r\n2. Set a widget for Focus Nightly.\r\n3. Resize the widget to 2x1.\r\n4. Observe the microphone icon placement.\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nThe microphone icon is placed on the right end of the widget.\r\n### Actual behavior\r\nThe microphone icon is incorrectly placed on towards the Firefox Focus logo.\r\nOn tablet, this issue only occurs in landscape mode.\r\n### Device information\r\n\r\n* Android device: Google Pixel 6 (Android 13), Lenovo Yoga Tab 11 (Android 11).\r\n* Focus version: latest Focus Nightly 106.0a1 from 08/24.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/89388888/186596521-2198689b-5227-48d2-b40a-4c6a0adf07f5.JPG\" width=\"40%\" />\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/89388888/186596639-41482492-a1c3-48db-b758-e77f44440a32.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n",
